snippet.textDisplay: Dear Dr Cambell. I have been watching your videos with considerable interest. I echo many comments on here by saying that you explain things in simplistic terms that are easy to understand.  Your knowledge is of huge help. Thank you for keeping us informed in a non sensational and fact based manner. It makes me feel very proud to have a fellow Brit (I’m not a doctor) help so many people around the globe. Stay well and please keep your superb videos rolling out. I hope everyone stays safe and well around the globe.
